title: [Museum Gallery, West Wing]
description: A gleaming set of crimson and golden plate, shaped to fit a woman's form, hangs on a rack.  Beside it hangs a painting, framed in solid gold.  In the center of the room, a model of a campsite sits on a large, round table.
